The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                               Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , August 2 , 2009                
	Get-together    Join Chini Adda at The School of Chinese Language, Sunny Park, 4pm to 6pm.        
	Kids fair    Check out Kids Fair 2009 at Ice Skating Rink, 10.30am to 8pm.        
	Workshop    Attend a national workshop titled Sri Aurobindos Political Life, The Alipore Bomb Trial and His Uttarpara Speech  A Centennial Perspective at Bhasha Bhavan, 10am to 5pm.         
	Songs    Enjoy an evening of Tagores songs to be presented by Aditi Mohsin of Bangladesh at Netaji Bhawan, 7pm.         
	Theatre    Be there at the staging of Manoj Mitras Ja Nei Bharatey at Academy of Fine Arts, 6.30pm.     
	Eye on art    Browse through A Monsoon Mosaic, an exhibition of paintings and sketches, at The Art Shoppe Gallery, 11am to 7pm.    Move on to Vision, a group exhibition at Academy of Fine Arts, Central Gallery, 3pm to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                                   
